468eb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://blog.goo.ne.jp/vanillaic ... 9262d82fc28ca8468eb</a><br><a href=\"https://blog.goo.ne.jp/biting_angle/e/a81944e38acc164fb932f6619431547e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://blog.goo.ne.jp/biting_an ... 64fb932f6619431547e</a><br>视频：<br><a href=\"http://v.qiye10000.com/v/XNuImMuQuNvq.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://v.qiye10000.com/v/XNuImMuQuNvq.html</a>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/41/64189.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1337676","time":"2018-4-15 20:13","userId":"syz4521233","userName":"syz","userSign":"","message":"正解厉害了～"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/78/277873.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1337739","time":"2018-4-15 22:52","userId":"277873","userName":"KooGospel","userSign":"","message":"优秀干货！"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/04/300439.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1337735","time":"2018-4-15 22:36","userId":"temori","userName":"Temori","userSign":"(それとも酔いどれの千夜一夜)","message":"去看了原视频，被冈田的解释感动到了，我再按原文翻译一下。<br>这个时候的人类大概已经不懂日语了。举个例子，我们跟外国人说话的时候，他们看到日本人可能会边说“どうも、こんにちは”边双手合十行礼。这只是佛教徒的行礼方式，日本人是不会这么打招呼的。但我们看到这个，比起失望，更会边心里想着“日本人是不会这么做的呀”，边苦笑着被对方的心意感动。“感动”从本质上来说，不是百分百的感动，而更是含有着5%或是10%的苦楚的同时，仍然会为双方的心意而感动。我们想做出这种感觉，所以就把イ给反过来写了。这么一来，（在片中）人类可能已经灭绝了，可能人类文明被其他的种族所继承下来，但（他们）仍然想传达出这种感谢之情。除此之外，更重要的是，对于从这么远的地方归来的人，想对她们说一声“欢迎回家”。我们想在片尾的イ里将科幻和情感结合起来传达给观众。<br>我认为在这个地方的小小斟酌，就是科幻，就是GAINAX的标志，也是飞跃巅峰的主题。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/69/6912.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1337736","time":"2018-4-15 22:47","userId":"6912","userName":"tora","userSign":"","message":"好赞！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/06/360675.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1337750","time":"2018-4-15 23:45","userId":"blackadder","userName":"Blackadder","userSign":"","message":"真是精彩"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/16/361639.jpg","floor":"#6-3","id":"1337756","time":"2018-4-16 00:05","userId":"361639","userName":"发光的球","userSign":"","message":"之前的讨论有人提到所谓gainax的人文关怀，大概如此了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/41/54176.jpg","floor":"#6-4","id":"1337782","time":"2018-4-16 03:22","userId":"light_44","userName":"lighthouse","userSign":"","message":"那么厉害，是时候补飞越巅峰了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/99/299900.jpg","floor":"#6-5","id":"1337783","time":"2018-4-16 03:26","userId":"299900","userName":"Oshino","userSign":"","message":"好棒"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3417.jpg","floor":"#6-6","id":"1337791","time":"2018-4-16 07:46","userId":"venusxx","userName":"Venusxx","userSign":"","message":"好"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#6-7","id":"1337792","time":"2018-4-16 07:50","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">lighthouse</span> 说: 那么厉害，是时候补飞越巅峰了</q></div>我推荐合体剧场版 一次就可以补两部"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1337793","time":"2018-4-16 07:55","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/ep/7071#post_461724\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://bgm.tv/ep/7071#post_461724</a><br>其实去原帖讨论更多","sub":[]}]